  <brief_title>Preoperative Pain, Function, and Activity for Total Hip and Knee Arthroplasty Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Influence of Preoperative Pain, Function, and Activity on Time to Fulfill Discharge Criteria for Total Hip and Knee Arthroplasty Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
